# Architecture & Tech Stack
- Next.js App Router (React Server Components by default)
- Strictly TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS & shadcn/ui for styling
- Vercel AI SDK for AI Orchestration
- Zod for all data validation and LLM structured outputs

# Core Philosophy: Schema-First & JSON-Driven
- The entire system is driven by strict JSON schemas. 
- Never build hardcoded, monolithic pages. Build modular UI components that map to JSON keys.
- Separate business logic (Server Actions, Scrapers, AI prompts) strictly from the UI layer.

# Development Rules
- Keep components atomic and modular.
- Optimize for 100/100 Lighthouse scores: minimal client-side JavaScript, favor Server Components.
- When generating AI outputs, always use `generateObject` or `streamObject` from the Vercel AI SDK with a predefined Zod schema.